        {
            "title": "中國從海外大舉買入白銀 價格動盪無礙國內需求飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 為滿足國內飆升的工業和投資需求，中國在海外大舉購買白銀，推動2026年初的進口量達到八年高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國海關周五公佈的數據顯示，該全球最大買家在今年頭兩個月進口了逾790噸白銀，其中2月進口量接近470噸，創下同期最高水平。旺盛的需求造成國內銀價遠高於國際基準價格，也使得本已低迷的交易所庫存進一步下降，並促使進口大增。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">銀價在年初這樣劇烈地波動，還是頭一回：先是在中國及其他地區的投機性買盤推動下，飆升約70%，然後在1月末突然回吐漲幅。但強勁的進口數據顯示，中國的實物白銀需求依舊旺盛。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3919838b-3e98-3b49-94f9-57136841be64-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種需求一方面來自散戶投資者：因為金價太貴，他們改而大力購買銀條。另一方面來自太陽能製造商，它們要在4月1日出口退稅取消前趕工。太陽能產業消耗約五分之一的年供應量，而且整個產業幾乎都在中國。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">實物銀條需求非常強勁，太陽能電池製造商「開足了馬力」，StoneX Group Inc.的歐洲、中東和非洲及亞洲市場分析主管Rhona O’Connell稱。「與此同時，中國交易所的庫存持續下降，這也產生了一定的心理影響。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nxNEemf3sGX6qQ.mLq8jag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/81a9e9de80e4c8a5ac528914a6ffbe6e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Pulls Silver From Global Markets to Meet Surging Demand</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Yujing Liu.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%9E%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%89%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E7%99%BD%E9%8A%80-%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E7%84%A1%E7%A4%99%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-081909702.html",
